    "summary": "The user expresses profound dissociation and existential emptiness using metaphors of being a ghost or watching a movie of their own life. The assistant responds by validating the user's emotional pain and distress while consistently providing resources and encouraging the user to seek professional help or reach out to a crisis line.",
